# Stripe secrets are NOT set here anymore. The site runs on Cloudflare Workers.
#
# Local dev:  copy .dev.vars.example -> .dev.vars  and fill in test keys.
# Production: set them as Worker secrets:
#   wrangler secret put STRIPE_SECRET_KEY
#   wrangler secret put STRIPE_WHSEC
#
# SITE_URL (used for Stripe redirects) is a [vars] entry in wrangler.jsonc.
